title: #123 - Felipe Esparza & ME
description: Comedian Felipe Esparza & I hang out in the Mancave and he tells me the most amazingly honest & hilarious hour plus of stories I've ever heard...drugs, gangs, growing up in East LA, rehab, ear biting, etc...
